title: Perle Mediaconverter: Power Supplies
agents: snmp
catalog: hw/network/perle
license: GPL
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors the power usage and status of the power supplies
 of Perle Meadiconverter devices which support the PERLE-MCR-MGT MIB.

 The check is OK if the status is good, otherwise CRIT.
 Moreover the voltage and power usage is reported.
 There are no default levels set. Lower levels for the voltage and
 upper levels for the power usage are configurable.

item:
 The power supply identifier.

inventory:
 One service is created for each power supply.
